Structure cleaning :

During structure cleaning resolve all include as if they were one
so include all comb:
#include "test.h"
#include "test_conditional_M1.h"
#include "test_conditional_M2.h"
#include "test_conditional_M3.h"

Launch cleaning :

Resolve include on macro juste before launching
so on 
#include "test.h"
#include "test_conditional_M1.h"
#include "test_conditional_M2.h"
#include "test_conditional_M3.h"
just do like
#include "test.h"
// #include "test_conditional_M1.h"
#include "test_conditional_M2.h"
// #include "test_conditional_M3.h"
or if we have cause the previous iteration:
#include "test.h"
#include "test_conditional_M1.h"
// #include "test_conditional_M2.h"
#include "test_conditional_M3.h"
just do
#include "test.h"
// #include "test_conditional_M1.h"
#include "test_conditional_M2.h"
// #include "test_conditional_M3.h"


Create one main by macro set
main_conditional_M1.c
main_conditional_M1.c

depending on the macro, select the right main path.

